<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ripe-adj">ripe <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /raɪp/    美 /raɪp/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(果、谷等) 成熟的；时机成熟的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>ripe apples 
成熟的苹果</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>The time is ripe for</strong> a reform. 
改革的时机已经成熟。</p></div></div>